_Dubai, UAE_

*Main requirements:*
- At least 3 years of experience with Python and R for Data Analysis

- bupaR library (R)

- Vensim software package

- agent-based modeling

- Working on business process optimization of huge organizations

- Creating predictive models of a time spent per specific task
- Delivering insights which can increase productivity based on data
- Analyzing and organizing huge amounts of unstructured event data

*Salary:* 10k$ per month (tax-free)
*Benefits*: visa, flight to Dubai, hotel stay for 2 weeks, insurance.
